OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774966279
OL,3,CSycamore Gap 'Tree of Hope' planted in
OL,4,CSouth Downs National Park
OL,6,FA "Tree of Hope" grown from the iconic
OL,7,FSycamore Gap tree on Hadrian's Wall
OL,8,Fhas been planted in the South Downs
OL,9,FNational Park.
OL,11,FCommunity leaders gathered next to
OL,12,FSwanbourne Lake in Arundel, to plant
OL,13,Fthe tree from seeds taken from the
OL,14,Foriginal Sycamore Gap tree that was
OL,15,Fillegally felled in Northumberland
OL,16,FNational Park in 2023.
OL,26,@nD@COUnD@PO]
