FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774966279
OL,3,CSycamore Gap 'Tree of Hope' planted in
OL,4,CSouth Downs National Park
OL,6,FSince then, new shoots have emerged
OL,7,Fand 49 saplings ` one for each foot of
OL,8,Fthe tree's height ` have been nurtured
OL,9,Fover the past two years by the
OL,10,FNational Trust's Plant Conservation
OL,11,FCentre.
OL,13,FEach of the UK's 15 National Parks has
OL,14,Fbeen gifted a "tree of hope" as
OL,15,Fsymbols of nature recovery, and this
OL,16,Fwill mark 16 years since the South
OL,17,FDowns National Park was created.
OL,19,FThe tree in the South Downs was
OL,20,Fplanted with kind permission of His
OL,21,FGrace, the Duke of Norfolk.
OL,26,@vD@OOUvD@\O]
