FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774966279
OL,3,CSycamore Gap 'Tree of Hope' planted in
OL,4,CSouth Downs National Park
OL,6,FHis Grace said: "We are delighted to
OL,7,Freceive this historic sycamore tree
OL,8,Fand plant it by Swanbourne Lake where
OL,9,Fwe hope it will be visited and enjoyed
OL,10,Fby many people for years to come."
OL,12,FVanessa Rowlands, Chair of the South
OL,13,FDowns National Park Authority, said:
OL,14,F"It's incredible to think that this
OL,15,Fbeautiful tree has been grown from the
OL,16,FSycamore Gap tree and it just shows
OL,17,Fhow nature can bounce back and recover.
OL,26,@nD@QOUrD@bO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
