FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774966279
OL,3,CSycamore Gap 'Tree of Hope' planted in
OL,4,CSouth Downs National Park
OL,6,F"National Parks are about bringing
OL,7,Fpeople together and finding a
OL,8,Fconnection with nature, so we are
OL,9,Freally pleased to plant this tree as
OL,10,Fwe celebrate the birthday of the South
OL,11,FDowns National Park.
OL,13,F"I hope this tree touches as many
OL,14,Flives as the original Sycamore Gap
OL,15,Ftree did and spreads positivity, hope
OL,16,Fand joy."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@IO]
